title: Wild-Card Weekend Reaction Part 1
description:
Kevin Clark and Ryen Russillo provide their immediate reactions and analysis to the Buffalo Bills' first playoff win in 25 years (0:43), the Rams' upset win on the road against the Seahawks (11:24), and the Tampa Bay Bucs defeating the Washington Football Team (21:30).
